1. *Čak* i on je učestvovao na proslavi. (Even he participated in the celebration.)
2. Za sada je *čak* i prekoračen budžet. (The budget has even been exceeded so far.)
3. Svi su zaboravili, *čak* i on. (Everyone forgot, even him.)
4. Ništa nismo postigli, *čak* ni malo. (We achieved nothing, not even a little.)
5. U našem selu je *čak* i Internet. (There's even Internet in our village.)
6. *Čak* i ja mislim da je to dobra ideja. (Even I think that's a good idea.)